Gedit 3 Whitespace Remover
=================================

Author: Alexandr Grigorcea <cahr.gr@gmail.com>
Home:   <https://github.com/cahrgr/Gedit-Whitespace-Remover>

License
-------

See the LICENSE file.

Install
-------
Copy files whitespace-remover.py and whitespace-remover.plugin
in  /usr/share/gedit/plugins/
Copy file whitespace-remover.gschema.xml
in /usr/share/glib-2.0/schemas/ and run as root (or sudo)
$ glib-compile-schemas /usr/share/glib-2.0/schemas

Activate the plugin from gedit Preferences
